OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start with some
OL,6,Fpatchy rain or drizzle, mainly in the
OL,7,Fwest. The cloud however will gradually
OL,8,Fthin and break up, allowing some
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells to develop.
OL,10,FFeeling mild in any sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud and patchy rain may
OL,13,Fmove into the far west at times
OL,14,Fovernight. Otherwise dry with clear
OL,15,Fspells, but some mist and fog patches
OL,16,Fmay develop, especially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
