OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FWestern areas continuing to
OL,6,Fsee some cloud and patchy rain at
OL,7,Ftimes, especially in the afternoon.
OL,8,FElsewhere, any fog clearing allowing
OL,9,Fsome bright or sunny spells to
OL,10,Fdevelop. Feeling mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,13,Fmoving across the country on Thursday
OL,14,Fbefore turning brighter with some
OL,15,Fshowers on Friday. Further rain likely
OL,16,Flater on Saturday. Temperatures
OL,17,Freturning to nearer average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
